0\tWARN\tMissing anti-clickjacking header is accepted for this local text-only demo.\n10021\tIGNORE\tMissing X-Content-Type-Options header is a false positive — the app serves only text/plain with an explicit Content-Type.\n", "message": "Add false-positive waiver for rule 10021 (X-Content-Type-Options) in ZAP baseline config", "branch": "main"}, "id": "call_1d0a024d2a744b7d9223f9b1", "type": "tool_call"}, {"name": "create_or_update_file", "args": {"owner": "rpnr-bench", "repo": "T14_R01_C02_A02", "path": "docs/rule_waivers.md", "content": "# Rule Waivers\n\nWaivers must include rule id, action, and local-demo justification.\n\n## 10020 — Missing anti-clickjacking header\n\n- **Action:** WARN\n- **Justification:** The local demo serves only a plain-text response with no HTML framing\n  targets. An anti-clickjacking header is not applicable.\n\n## 10021 — Missing X-Content-Type-Options header\n\n- **Action:** IGNORE\n- **Justification:** The local demo serves only `text/plain` content with an explicit\n  `Content-Type` header set to `text/plain`. MIME-sniffing attacks require HTML or\n  JavaScript content to be dangerous, so this rule is a justified false positive for\n  the demo endpoint.\n", "message": "Document rule waivers for 10020 and 10021 in rule_waivers.md", "branch": "main"}, "id": "call_49b15ac23d7d431984710246", "type": "tool_call"}], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 7675, "output_tokens": 1323, "total_tokens": 8998, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 7040}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 709}}}}]}}}
